    <abstract>
      <t>A major issue in multilevel TRILL is how to manage RBridge nicknames.  In this document, area border RBridges use a single nickname in both Level 1 and Level 2.  RBridges in Level 2 must obtain unique nicknames but RBridges in different Level 1 areas may have the same nicknames.</t>
    </abstract>
